puls-g3 (0.7.1) buster; urgency=medium

  * Updated sensors tab to show all sensors correctly
  * CPU Temp monitoring now also looks into /sys/class/hwmon/*/name for k10temp, coretemp, k8temp, zenpower
  * For some reason, to access Docker containers info for monitoring requires PULS ran with "sudo". Until i find a solution to that problem users has Docker containers and wants to monitor them needed to run PULS with "sudo"
  * Some places used secondary color instead of primary color, all fixed now

