puls-g3 (0.6.2) buster; urgency=medium

  * Added a new feature to view Docker container logs directly in the UI (press 'l' in the containers tab)
  * Release executable PULS file now opens terminal for itself, result is working like AppImage application but executable way
  * Updated bollard to v0.19 and refactored codebase to fix legacy client errors and support newer Docker APIs
  * (I hope) Fixed 0Hz/0Usage reporting on AMD cards by implementing a fallback to hwmon sensors when legacy pp_dpm_* files are missing
  * Removed unused "add implementation later" code and parameters, resolving compiler warnings and lowering binary size

